data.chText: （建筑群中间或后面的）小街，小巷，胡同
data.enText: a narrow passage behind or between buildings

data.chText: 狭窄的 / 黑暗的小巷

tr: a narrow street with walls on both sides
a lane down which a bowling ball is rolled toward pins

value.def: An alley is a narrow passage or street with buildings or walls on both sides.
